HEADWORD: Polypous
<hw>Pol"y*pous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>polypeux</ets>. See <er>Polyp</er>.]</ety> <def>Of the nature of a
